NK010(tha)003:0: phur pa rgyud lugs las brgyud pa'i gsol 'debs byin rlabs shing rta bzhugs /
NK010(tha)003:1: byang chub rdo rje rigs lnga lcam dral dang //
NK010(tha)003:2: bde ba'i 'khor lo rig 'dzin rdo rje chos //
NK010(tha)003:3: pra b+ha hasti sangs rgyas pad+ma skyes //
NK010(tha)003:4: bstan pa'i chu 'go dgongs brda' snyan brgyud la //
NK010(tha)003:5: gsol ba 'debs so byin rlabs char chen phob //
NK010(tha)003:6: bi ma la dang bal po many+dzu sh+r+ai //
NK010(tha)003:7: rdo rje sems ma 'gar ston shes rab 'byung //
NK010(tha)003:8: chos kyi rgyal po tshangs pa'i me tog sogs //
NK010(tha)003:9: rgyal lugs brgyud pa'i bla ma thams cad la //
NK010(tha)003:10: gsol ba 'debs so jo mo mkhar chen bza' dang cog ro bza' //
NK010(tha)003:11: dpal gyi dbang phyug ngam 'bre a tsar sa //
NK010(tha)003:12: smad las rtsal thon lag lhag byang chub sogs //
NK010(tha)003:13: jo lcam brgyud pa'i bla ma thams cad la //
NK010(tha)003:14: gsol ba 'debs so rdo rje bdud 'joms a tsar dpal me tog /
NK010(tha)003:15: rdo rje gzhon nu zhang zhung yon tan grags //
NK010(tha)003:16: yon tan rin chen kun mkhyen rong zom sogs //
NK010(tha)003:17: sna nam brgyud pa'i bla ma thams cad la //
NK010(tha)003:18: gsol ba 'debs so phyi yul snang char dgra bgegs gnyis la thebs //
NK010(tha)003:19: sems med 'byung ba chu yang cham la phab //
NK010(tha)003:20: gnyags lo mchog dang lha dpal 'o bran sogs //
NK010(tha)003:21: sham sngon brgyud pa'i bla ma thams cad la //
NK010(tha)003:22: gsol ba 'debs so nang du rang rgyud nyon mongs dug lngar thebs //
NK010(tha)003:23: mtshan ma rdzas kyi phung pas mu stegs btul //
NK010(tha)003:24: rnal 'byor dbang phyug 'dar phyar la sogs pa //
NK010(tha)003:25: dpal chen phur pa'i grub thob thams cad la //
NK010(tha)003:27: don dam byang chub sems kyi phur pa ni //
NK010(tha)003:28: rtogs pa chos sku'i ngang nas dgongs brgyud dang //
NK010(tha)003:29: rig 'dzin mkha' 'gro'i brda' las snyan brgyud rdzogs //
NK010(tha)003:30: pad+mas lung bstan 'jigs med gling pa la //
NK010(tha)003:31: gsol ba 'debs so phrin las 'od zer 'jigs med chos kyi grags //
NK010(tha)003:32: gzhan phan mtha' yas thub bstan rgyal mtshan dpal //
NK010(tha)003:33: dpal ldan chos grags phan bde'i 'od zer zhabs //
NK010(tha)003:34: gsol ba 'debs so kha skong sh+lo ka 'di dz+ny+aa nas so //
NK010(tha)003:35: bdag nyid rtsa ba'i dkyil 'khor yab yum dang //
NK010(tha)003:36: sras mchog rigs lnga phur pa rdzas kyi lha //
NK010(tha)003:37: phyogs bcu khro bo'i dkyil 'khor khra thabs dang //
NK010(tha)003:38: dkyil 'khor mu ran skyong ba'i phur srung la //
NK010(tha)003:39: gsol ba 'debs so nad gdon bar chad sol //
NK010(tha)003:40: dbang phyug brgyad ldan rdo rje slob dpon gyis //
NK010(tha)003:41: rigs dbang lnga dang lha dbang zhe gnyis kyi //
NK010(tha)003:42: rdul tshon dkyil 'khor chen por smin byas nas //
NK010(tha)003:43: skye gnas bzhi yi bag chags sbyong tshul las //
NK010(tha)003:44: gzugs phung rtsa dang bcas pa'i snang zhen kun //
NK010(tha)003:45: lhar snang phyag rgya chen por smin par shog /
NK010(tha)003:46: bla ma yab yum rdo rje phung po'i grong //
NK010(tha)003:47: zhu bde'i 'gros kyis drangs ba'i byang chub sems //
NK010(tha)003:48: dus sbyor bcu gnyis rlung gi gshed gyur nas //
NK010(tha)003:49: sgra grags shes rab dbyangs kyi rol mo 'khrol //
NK010(tha)003:50: rlung khams yi ge'i gdangs su grol bar shog /
NK010(tha)003:51: bde ba'i bdag nyid ri dwags mig can ma //
NK010(tha)003:52: pad+ma b+hany+dza mok+sha la sbyar bas //
NK010(tha)003:53: dga' ba rnam bzhis drangs pa'i dpe'i ye shes //
NK010(tha)003:54: snang mched thob pa'i pha mthar mthong bar shog /
NK010(tha)003:55: rnam thar gsum gyi dkyil 'khor la brten nas //
NK010(tha)003:56: don gyi ye shes phyag rgya chen po'i dbyings //
NK010(tha)003:57: rnam par mi rtog mthong lam dang 'grogs nas //
NK010(tha)003:58: sa bcu'i rgyun mtha' rdo rje phur pa'i zhal //
NK010(tha)003:59: da lta nyid du mthong bar byin gyis rlobs //
NK010(tha)003:60: stod las la brten rig 'dzin rnam pa bzhi'i //
NK010(tha)003:61: go 'phang mngon gyur rtogs pas bdag rgyud bsgral //
NK010(tha)003:62: smad las la brten thugs rjes gzhan sgrol ba'i //
NK010(tha)003:63: phrin las rnam bzhi lhun gyis grub par shog /
NK010(tha)003:64: ces pa'ang bla brang dpal sdings pa dang /
NK010(tha)003:65: yang zhabs pas bskul ba'i ngor /
